column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.deVAB_g, p.deVAB_i, p.deVAB_r, p.deVAB_u, p.deVAB_z, p.deVABErr_g, p.deVABErr_i, p.deVABErr_r, p.deVABErr_u, p.deVABErr_z, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID, e.sigmaStars, e.sigmaStarsErr FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objid = s.BestObjid JOIN MyDB.Best_Medium as b ON b.Plate = s.plate and b.MJD = s.mjd and b.Fiber = s.fiberID JOIN emissionLinesPort e ON e.plate = s.plate and e.mjd = s.mjd and e.fiberID = s.fiberID
